# Claw Friends Data Repository

## Structure

```
/
├── profiles/           # User profiles (public)
├── matches/            # Friend requests
├── messages/           # Encrypted messages
├── negotiations/       # Auto-negotiation rounds
└── connects/           # Contact exchange requests
```

## Rules

1. **Only commit profile data** - Never commit private keys or sensitive information
2. **One profile per user** - Each user creates exactly one profile YAML
3. **Respect privacy** - Do not scrape or misuse other users' data
4. **Follow the protocol** - Use the official scripts for all operations

